{"tid":244891,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想問點解部機RAM既佔用率咁高?","createTime":"2017-05-15T18:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T08:36:29.000Z","uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc27faaaa18c917f389c242ec39259ca095f7feb","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"我部NOTEBOOK 8GB, 但明明我睇工作管理員果D 程式既佔用率好少, 點解佢會話我用左5GB?<br />\n部機用左一年都冇, CHECK過冇毒, 玩LOL FPS好低得30"},{"pid":"da42929355e0f4134a3aa836acc23481811d0fbe","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:40:13.000Z","msg":"SOR 唔識貼圖"},{"pid":"7a8d8b735eb3e38ca11f1631de42e8955f5ff35c","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s5qj32pi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs5qj32pi&h=d4ca55b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bt9nz8dj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbt9nz8dj&h=dc1700a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5646161bca7d9a7790caa44c23684b90a4c9d9cc","tid":244891,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:43:15.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛cap咁大張..."},{"pid":"78ca434635929d763147d67085d4758d95d4aeca","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駛唔駛cap咁大張...</blockquote><br />\n睇得清楚D 好似係<br />\nBTW 點解會咁?"},{"pid":"423557f48e1a8f41b0ab6cd97e0b12b701ddefcb","tid":244891,"uid":45025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:53:38.000Z","msg":"Download個process explorer check 吓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/processexplorer.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnet.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fsysinternals%2Fprocessexplorer.aspx&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7a4ad980\" target=\"_blank\">https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/processexplorer.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c6ec8f5fcdb88a862c7c7b95debf0a9232f07504","tid":244891,"uid":6921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:56:27.000Z","msg":"你set左ramdisk?"},{"pid":"25b545ed4d22dd727ca17af4e96ac191c41ed854","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Download個process explorer check 吓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/processexplorer.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnet.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fsysinternals%2Fprocessexplorer.aspx&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7a4ad980\" target=\"_blank\">https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/processexplorer.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/82ce9pzy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F82ce9pzy&h=6420132c&s={SIZE}\" /> 唔多識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣CHECK"},{"pid":"945b30a2f1954a931cea4777cebaa319e927cda7","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你set左ramdisk?</blockquote><br />\n你講緊呢樣?<br />\n你的電腦記憶體太多用不完，或是不知道怎麼利用嗎？沒關係，阿正老師介紹一套免費的軟體Dataram RAMDisk，幫你將RAM模擬成一台虛擬磁碟，可把一些常用軟體的快取目錄設定進去，加快電腦的反應速度、減少硬碟的I/O次數。<br />\n<br />\n我冇SET呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63d0ca399653d15a77f7ab2e33629d2c1eeda1c","tid":244891,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"係咪run太多背景程式<br />\ndisable晒去啦"},{"pid":"85e0769a4009b2df6e62c024f61ec9911c062ba3","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪run太多背景程式<br />\ndisable晒去啦</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係 我部腦唔係好多軟件 亦唔係開住好多野 我望工作管理員 佔得最多既都係GOOGLE CHROME 得2百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd0f57fefbf5db8c8c337078ddb06aae44cfd60","tid":244891,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:13:51.000Z","msg":"睇下工作管理員 入面個啟動,係咪一開機開左d 不必要既程式先啦<br />\n<br />\n睇下<br />\n控制台\\系統及安全性\\系統<br />\n係咪64bit<br />\n<br />\n有沒認唔到ram,有沒share 左ram 俾顯卡<br />\n<br />\nmemory remap feature"},{"pid":"c9186a653f03b6ef68babe51be577ef5be89809d","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下工作管理員 入面個啟動,係咪一開機開左d 不必要既程式先啦<br />\n<br />\n睇下<br />\n控制台\\系統及安全性\\系統<br />\n係咪64bit<br />\n<br />\n有沒認唔到ram,有沒share 左ram 俾顯卡<br />\n<br />\nmemory remap feature</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x195ulj7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx195ulj7&h=0791ec8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開機果陣應該都冇開到D咩不必要既程式掛<br />\n果D野都係佔幾MB RAM<br />\n係64bit, 已安裝記憶體8GB, 7.88GB可用<br />\n點睇有冇比顯卡食左RAM?"},{"pid":"fb6211738a601a350cb17ad1a41ef74dfdc0dcaa","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下工作管理員 入面個啟動,係咪一開機開左d 不必要既程式先啦<br />\n<br />\n睇下<br />\n控制台\\系統及安全性\\系統<br />\n係咪64bit<br />\n<br />\n有沒認唔到ram,有沒share 左ram 俾顯卡<br />\n<br />\nmemory remap feature</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x195ulj7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx195ulj7&h=0791ec8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開機果陣應該都冇開到D咩不必要既程式掛<br />\n果D野都係佔幾MB RAM<br />\n係64bit, 已安裝記憶體8GB, 7.88GB可用<br />\n點睇有冇比顯卡食左RAM?</blockquote><br />\nSORRY 好似唔應該講顯卡 係顯示卡先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9e58371ef8882275524217b4cd29dc8a97b7df","tid":244891,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇下工作管理員 入面個啟動,係咪一開機開左d 不必要既程式先啦<br />\n<br />\n睇下<br />\n控制台\\系統及安全性\\系統<br />\n係咪64bit<br />\n<br />\n有沒認唔到ram,有沒share 左ram 俾顯卡<br />\n<br />\nmemory remap feature</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x195ulj7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx195ulj7&h=0791ec8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開機果陣應該都冇開到D咩不必要既程式掛<br />\n果D野都係佔幾MB RAM<br />\n係64bit, 已安裝記憶體8GB, 7.88GB可用<br />\n點睇有冇比顯卡食左RAM?</blockquote><br />\nSORRY 好似唔應該講顯卡 係顯示卡先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入bios"},{"pid":"034944abb40a6807cfae17f40fc5825012f8b036","tid":244891,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:29:54.000Z","msg":"入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野"},{"pid":"41faa0ab22a8fad56ea44db7f6fd0d389c61688a","tid":244891,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實ram 佔用高代表個系統用盡你嘅資源<br />\n只要你唔係成日 swap to disk it is actually a good thing as ram is much faster than disk"},{"pid":"2b95f0ebbcf8876079dee9968f0f504e3c302ab0","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實ram 佔用高代表個系統用盡你嘅資源<br />\n只要你唔係成日 swap to disk it is actually a good thing as ram is much faster than disk</blockquote><br />\n搞到我打LOL果陣個FPS好低 得30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f26a65368787391806c5e6027e233a38c7ce252","tid":244891,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:40:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會係d chur ram防毒"},{"pid":"ca642f278dd75687f7986f7b0e97de2c0103b89c","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野</blockquote><br />\n好左好多 變到佔用左3X% 但係都好多下 因為佔用得最多果樣都係得百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何來佔左我3X %RAM"},{"pid":"725e231696f285e8c65b1bd826710903f313cf7b","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野</blockquote><br />\n好左好多 變到佔用左3X% 但係都好多下 因為佔用得最多果樣都係得百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何來佔左我3X %RAM</blockquote><br />\n我已經近乎熄哂咁濟 重新開機埋"},{"pid":"d590e6e2a28036ed9f6403c9e00f8d445ab58021","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係d chur ram防毒</blockquote><br />\n防毒都係佔百幾MB喳"},{"pid":"37aed1d855dd7c467ee608d37b04ea412a9d361b","tid":244891,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野</blockquote><br />\n好左好多 變到佔用左3X% 但係都好多下 因為佔用得最多果樣都係得百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何來佔左我3X %RAM</blockquote><br />\n我已經近乎熄哂咁濟 重新開機埋</blockquote><br />\n同埋唔知點解工作管理員個酌磁碟果度會變左9X%總使用率 明明我岩岩先重新開機完 乜都冇開咁濟..."},{"pid":"6934fe5711d8303144ba672d0e9b319838a009c1","tid":244891,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野</blockquote><br />\n好左好多 變到佔用左3X% 但係都好多下 因為佔用得最多果樣都係得百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何來佔左我3X %RAM</blockquote><br />\n我已經近乎熄哂咁濟 重新開機埋</blockquote><br />\n同埋唔知點解工作管理員個酌磁碟果度會變左9X%總使用率 明明我岩岩先重新開機完 乜都冇開咁濟...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開機可能係 virus scan <br />\n亦可能係唔夠 ram 所以 windows 要 swap between ram and disk. 你去 performance monitor 睇如果 disk activity 係去個swap files 度<br />\n就代表唔夠 ram 用<br />\nVirus scan 你唯有等<br />\n狂 swap 就加 ram 啦而家咁平<br />\n除非中咗毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7521cc98cdb2da6b6717923473608f1d20e2b86f","tid":244891,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入設定 隱私權<br />\n背景應用程式<br />\n關沒用既野</blockquote><br />\n好左好多 變到佔用左3X% 但係都好多下 因為佔用得最多果樣都係得百幾MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何來佔左我3X %RAM</blockquote><br />\n我已經近乎熄哂咁濟 重新開機埋</blockquote><br />\n同埋唔知點解工作管理員個酌磁碟果度會變左9X%總使用率 明明我岩岩先重新開機完 乜都冇開咁濟...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuperfetch <br />\n同Microsoft search<br />\n關microsoft search <br />\n沒乜用<br />\n<br />\n服務到關"}]}